---
---
<section id="leaderboard">
  <div class="section-label">Leaderboard</div>

  <div class="lb-wrap">
    <div class="lb-left">
      <h2 class="lb-headline">Every point.<br><span>On record.</span></h2>
      <p class="lb-sub">
        Most sports have no memory. You play, you leave, nothing is logged. At PCI, every game is recorded. Every score, every format, every session. You build a ranking that travels with you - from your group, to your venue, to your city, and eventually, across India.
      </p>
      <p class="lb-sub" style="margin-top:16px;">
        The leaderboard isn't just a stat. It's your standing in the community. It determines tournament seeding, bragging rights, and how the game remembers you.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="lb-mockup">
      <div class="lb-mockup-header">
        <span class="lb-mockup-title">Inter(+) Evening Group · Casa De Padel</span>
        <span class="lb-mockup-period">July 2026</span>
      </div>
      <div class="lb-table">
        <div class="lb-row lb-row-head">
          <span class="lb-col-rank">#</span>
          <span class="lb-col-player">Player</span>
          <span class="lb-col-stat">Games</span>
          <span class="lb-col-stat">Points</span>
        </div>
        <div class="lb-row lb-row-top">
          <span class="lb-col-rank lb-num">01</span>
          <span class="lb-col-player">Player 1</span>
          <span class="lb-col-stat">18</span>
          <span class="lb-col-stat lb-points">342</span>
        </div>
        <div class="lb-row">
          <span class="lb-col-rank lb-num">02</span>
          <span class="lb-col-player">Player 2</span>
          <span class="lb-col-stat">16</span>
          <span class="lb-col-stat lb-points">298</span>
        </div>
        <div class="lb-row">
          <span class="lb-col-rank lb-num">03</span>
          <span class="lb-col-player">Player 3</span>
          <span class="lb-col-stat">17</span>
          <span class="lb-col-stat lb-points">271</span>
        </div>
        <div class="lb-row">
          <span class="lb-col-rank lb-num">04</span>
          <span class="lb-col-player">Player 4</span>
          <span class="lb-col-stat">14</span>
          <span class="lb-col-stat lb-points">244</span>
        </div>
        <div class="lb-row">
          <span class="lb-col-rank lb-num">05</span>
          <span class="lb-col-player">Player 5</span>
          <span class="lb-col-stat">15</span>
          <span class="lb-col-stat lb-points">219</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lb-mockup-footer">Live scores · Updated after every session</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- WHAT GETS TRACKED -->
  <div class="lb-tracks">
    <div class="lb-track">
      <div class="lb-track-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="lb-track-title">Scores per format</div>
      <div class="lb-track-desc">Americano, Mexicano, Tournament - each format tracked by its own rules. Points are calculated correctly for every game type.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="lb-track">
      <div class="lb-track-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="lb-track-title">Full history</div>
      <div class="lb-track-desc">Every game you've ever played at PCI is on record. Your best runs, win streaks, and how you've improved - all retrievable, forever.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="lb-track">
      <div class="lb-track-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"/><path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"/><path d="M4 22h16"/><path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20.24 7 22"/><path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20.24 17 22"/><path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="lb-track-title">Tournament seeding</div>
      <div class="lb-track-desc">Your leaderboard position determines how you're seeded in PCI tournaments. Consistent play earns you the matchups you deserve.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- THE LADDER -->
  <div class="lb-ladder">
    <div class="lb-ladder-eyebrow">The ranking ladder</div>
    <div class="lb-steps">
      <div class="lb-step lb-step-live">
        <div class="lb-step-name">Your Group</div>
        <div class="lb-step-eg">Inter(+) Evening Group</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lb-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="lb-step lb-step-live">
        <div class="lb-step-name">Venue</div>
        <div class="lb-step-eg">Casa De Padel</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lb-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="lb-step">
        <div class="lb-step-name">Area</div>
        <div class="lb-step-eg">Kharadi</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lb-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="lb-step">
        <div class="lb-step-name">City</div>
        <div class="lb-step-eg">Pune</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lb-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="lb-step">
        <div class="lb-step-name">State</div>
        <div class="lb-step-eg">Maharashtra</div>
      </div>
      <div class="lb-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="lb-step">
        <div class="lb-step-name">India</div>
        <div class="lb-step-eg">National</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="lb-ladder-note">Live at Group and Venue level from day one. Area, City, State and National rankings unlock as PCI expands.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- PCI APP CALLOUT -->
  <div class="lb-app">
    <div>
      <div class="lb-app-badge">PCI App · Coming Soon</div>
      <p class="lb-app-desc">
        Scores, rankings, and match history are just the start. The PCI App will bring every part of the community into one place - group chat, announcements, events, session galleries, and your personal record. Built for members, by PCI. <strong>Founding members get early access.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>
